1.Ona je čak hodala *tipom* koje je plesao Fred Astaire. (She even walked with the the same gait as Fred Astaire danced.)
2. On je vodio pozorišnu predstavu *tipom* dramatičnog dokumentarca. (He was leading a theatre performance in the style of a dramatic documentary.)
3. Njihovi koraci su se mešali *tipom* koji je stvorio mali vrtlog. (Their steps were mixed in a way that created a small whirlpool.)
4. Ona je odmah reagovala *tipom* koji je pokazivao da neće da prihvati njegovu verziju. (She reacted immediately in a way that showed she wouldn't accept his version.)
5. On je završio svoju rečenicu *tipom* koji je ukazivao na njenu krivicu. (He ended his sentence in a way that pointed to her guilt.)